President Donald J. Trump has announced his intent to appoint several individuals to be Members of the President's Council on Sports, Fitness, and Nutrition for two-year terms. The appointees include Mariano Rivera, Misty May-Treanor, Herschel Junior Walker, William Belichick, Johnny David Damon, Nan Hayworth, Natalie Gulbis, Kyle Frederick Snyder, Julie Teer, Brenda Larsen Becker, Mehmet Oz, Amy Bockerstette, Robert Charles Wilkins, Trevor Joseph Drinkwater, Shauna Rohbock, Chris Tisi, Jake Olson, Linda Yaccarino, Urban Meyer, Troy Vincent, Jennifer Pharr Davis, Scott Turner, Colby Covington, Mary Owen, Jorge Masvidal, Robert Goldman, Matthew Hesse, Ashlee Lundvall, and Samuel James Worthington, Jr.